show.description: The Royal Secret follows Ishita Malhotra, a wealthy heiress who conceals her identity to build a life and love based on merit, not money. But when betrayal by her boyfriend Jay Mehta and the manipulations of the cunning Rhea threaten her self-worth, Ishita rises to reclaim her power, name, and heart—one explosive revelation at a time.
